# Marketing Platform (Astro)

## Framework

- **Astro**: Static site generation
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 with shared design tokens
- **Components**: `.astro` files in `apps/marketing/src/components/`
- **Utilities**: Import from `@repo/ui-astro`

## Astro Components

```astro
---
// Frontmatter (runs at build time)
import { colors } from "@repo/ui-astro";
const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<h1 class="text-primary">{title}</h1>
```

## Content Collections

- Define schemas in `src/content/config.ts`
- Use `getCollection()` to query content
- Markdown/MDX files in `src/content/`

## SEO

- Use `<head>` for meta tags
- Add sitemap: `npx astro add sitemap`
- Add RSS: `npx astro add rss`
- Use canonical URLs

## Static Generation

- Pages in `src/pages/` use file-based routing
- Dynamic routes with `[param].astro`
- `getStaticPaths()` for dynamic route generation

## Styling

- Same Tailwind CSS v4 configuration as web
- CSS variables in global stylesheet
- Use design tokens from `@repo/ui-shared`

## Testing

- **Unit**: Vitest for utilities
- **E2E**: Playwright for critical paths

## Deployment

- Builds to `dist/` folder
- Deploy to any static host
- Use `npx astro add vercel/netlify/cloudflare` for adapters
